Title: S6 Ep. 230 Intern Whisperer 2022 Fan Favorites
Description:
Isabella Johnston is the founder of Employers 4 Change and the host of The Intern Whisperer Podcast. She shared, this is our second year for our annual Fan Favorite Podcast vote.  Our guests and listeners helped us hit 10,000+ downloads before Christmas. We are excited to announce the top three winners episodes for our Podbean audio downloads and top three Intern Whisperer YouTube video winners. 

IWS Audio Podcast winners are:

First Place - Victoria Yampolsky Ep. 222,

Second Place Albee Shanefelter Ep. 224, 

Third Place Matthew Brown Ep. 210

Employers 4 Change YouTube Video Podcast winners are:

First Place Bob Dixon Ep.190,

Second Place John Crossman Ep.194,

Third Place Johnny Williams Ep.108

Visit our blog (https://www.e4c.tech/post/juicy-news-2022-recap-and-milestones) page to see the top 10 shows and links to all the guest episodes. Check out our press release also. 

The Intern Whisperer Podcast is brought to you by Employers 4 Change - Increasing inclusion and diversity through #Skills-based #DEI #recruitment and #management for #interns and #employees alike. Sign up to be an #Employer4Change that invests in #intern #talent and #employees.
